        <h3>Buildertrend — best for residential drawing management</h3>
        <p>Buildertrend's document and drawing management supports residential construction workflows. Plans can be uploaded, organized by project, and accessed by field teams and subcontractors from the mobile app. Change log tracking records when drawings are updated, keeping everyone on the current version. For residential GCs who primarily work from PDF plan sets (rather than BIM models), Buildertrend's drawing tools are sufficient and have the advantage of being integrated with the broader project management platform.</p>
